snippet.title: Sonic Lost in Nightmare World - CGS 2021
snippet.description:
Sonic Lost in Nightmare World make the scrapped content of Sonic 1 reborn in the mania style, taking major inspiration from early classic Sonic prototypes and concepts!


Check the game as soon as the 18th hits!
https://chaogameshowcase.wixsite.com/cgs2021/games
